        <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(14, 14, 14); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;Dear {!Loop_Rooms.Contract__r.Account.FirstName} {!Loop_Rooms.Contract__r.Account.LastName},&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(14, 14, 14); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;We hope this message finds you well.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(14, 14, 14); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;As you may already know, {!$Record.Contract__r.Account.FirstName} {!$Record.Contract__r.Account.LastName} will be moving out of {!$Record.Property__r.Street__c} on {!$Record.Contract__r.Contract_End_Date__c}. While we will miss having them as part of our community, this change brings a unique opportunity for you to select a new member to join your household.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(14, 14, 14); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;Here’s how the process works:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;Find a New Flatmate:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt; You and your current flatmates have the first opportunity to find a new tenant for the available room. Whether it’s a friend, colleague, or someone from your network, this is your chance to choose someone who fits well with your lifestyles and dynamics. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;Submit Your Candidate:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt; Once you have identified a potential new flatmate, please submit their details to us for a general background check. Our sales team will handle this screening to ensure a smooth transition.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;Need Assistance?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt; If you are unable to find a suitable candidate within 2 weeks, don’t worry. Habyt will step in to help find a new occupant for the room.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(14, 14, 14); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;We will need the following details for your candidate:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(14, 14, 14); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(14, 14, 14); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Full Name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(14, 14, 14); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Contact Information&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(14, 14, 14); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Brief Introduction (optional, but helpful)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(14, 14, 14); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(14, 14, 14); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;You can send this information directly to &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:sales@habyt.com&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(17, 85, 204); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;sales@habyt.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(14, 14, 14); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(14, 14, 14); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;If you have any questions or need further assistance during this process, please do not hesitate to reach out to our team. We are here to support you and ensure a seamless transition.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(14, 14, 14); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;Thank you for your cooperation and for helping us create a welcoming and cohesive living environment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(14, 14, 14); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt;Best regards,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14.6667px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(14, 14, 14);&quot;&gt;The Habyt Team&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(14, 14, 14); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</text>
